WEBVTT

00:00:10.830 --> 00:00:17.340 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:13.730 line:80%
We finally found it.

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:14.810 line:80%
Yeah, this is it.

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:15.600 line:80%
Let's go.

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:16.800 line:80%
Stop right there.

00:00:21.870 --> 00:00:22.990 line:80%
Why is there someone else here?

00:00:22.990 --> 00:00:23.560 line:80%
Didn't you see him?

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:25.090 line:80%
Didn't you see him just now?

00:00:30.470 --> 00:00:31.800 line:80%
Put down the title deed,

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.190 line:80%
and I'll let you go.

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:46.260 line:80%
Not happening.

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:49.640 line:80%
I'm walking out loud and proud.

00:00:50.150 --> 00:00:51.680 line:80%
Try and stop me.

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:03.320 line:80%
You darn scoundrels.

00:01:03.620 --> 00:01:05.289 line:80%
Put it down now!

00:01:13.810 --> 00:01:15.280 line:80%
You nosy neighbors

00:01:15.310 --> 00:01:17.040 line:80%
really don't know when to quit.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:19.280 line:80%
All lining up for death, huh?

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.230 line:80%
Before you go anywhere,

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:22.839 line:80%
see if my broom

00:01:22.839 --> 00:01:23.800 line:80%
agrees!

00:01:34.589 --> 00:01:35.390 line:80%
Get over here.

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:36.720 line:80%
I dare you.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:38.460 line:80%
You old geezer.

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:40.670 line:80%
You run, I chase.
You're not going anywhere!

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:41.279 line:80%
Wait!

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:56.380 line:80%
Trying to run, huh?

00:01:56.839 --> 00:01:58.040 line:80%
You think you can run?

00:01:59.510 --> 00:02:00.360 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:01.200 line:80%
I'm not!

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:07.880 line:80%
You dare hit me?

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:09.160 line:80%
Yeah, you're exactly who I meant to hit!

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:10.760 line:80%
I... I'll teach you a lesson!

00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:11.870 line:80%
For doing evil!

00:02:11.890 --> 00:02:13.220 line:80%
I'll teach you a lesson!

00:02:13.830 --> 00:02:14.520 line:80%
For doing evil!

00:02:14.520 --> 00:02:15.380 line:80%
For doing evil!

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:16.430 line:80%
These blows don't miss.

00:02:16.430 --> 00:02:18.290 line:80%
Find somewhere to hide, now!

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:29.950 line:80%
You stubborn old fool.

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:49.430 line:80%
Take that! Take that!

00:02:50.390 --> 00:02:51.160 line:80%
Changyu!

00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:52.670 line:80%
Changyu, Changyu, quick!

00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:56.080 line:80%
[Fan]

00:02:53.150 --> 00:02:53.920 line:80%
Mrs. Zhuang.

00:02:53.990 --> 00:02:54.879 line:80%
Please look after Changning for me.

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:55.390 line:80%
Okay.

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:11.540 line:80%
Get lost!

00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:27.230 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:03:27.230 --> 00:03:28.160 line:80%
Listen to me!

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:35.510 line:80%
I dare any of you!

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.120 line:80%
Quick, come on.

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:45.920 line:80%
Changyu.

00:03:46.450 --> 00:03:47.850 line:80%
Stop hitting them.

00:03:48.230 --> 00:03:50.270 line:80%
Zhao has beaten them half to death.

00:03:50.430 --> 00:03:51.510 line:80%
If you step in,

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:53.640 line:80%
they're really not going to make it.

00:03:56.710 --> 00:03:58.070 line:80%
You never learn, do you?

00:03:59.040 --> 00:03:59.950 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.420 line:80%
Dear Miss Fan.

00:04:02.270 --> 00:04:03.410 line:80%
Please don't get the wrong idea.

00:04:03.410 --> 00:04:04.700 line:80%
We came this time

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:07.040 line:80%
because we heard you're getting married.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:08.160 line:80%
We're here to congratulate you.

00:04:08.160 --> 00:04:08.760 line:80%
Yeah, that's right.

00:04:08.760 --> 00:04:10.230 line:80%
W-We're here to congratulate you.

00:04:10.230 --> 00:04:12.290 line:80%
We're not here to take the title deed.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:18.400 line:80%
You call this offering congratulations,
coming armed like this?

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.199 line:80%
My husband was already injured,

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:22.020 line:80%
and you still ganged up on him!

00:04:22.230 --> 00:04:23.190 line:80%
No, no, no!

00:04:23.190 --> 00:04:24.400 line:80%
-We didn't!
-We really didn't!

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:25.960 line:80%
We didn't even lay a finger on him.

00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:26.870 line:80%
W-We didn't hurt him.

00:04:26.870 --> 00:04:27.870 line:80%
We didn't hit him.

00:04:32.310 --> 00:04:33.640 line:80%
But you frightened him.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.570 line:80%
And that's not acceptable either!

00:04:35.570 --> 00:04:36.920 line:80%
Please don't. Don't.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.920 line:80%
So this is your esteemed husband.

00:04:47.230 --> 00:04:48.750 line:80%
We didn't know
who we were dealing with.

00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:49.820 line:80%
We truly didn't.

00:04:50.070 --> 00:04:51.600 line:80%
Money. Bring out the money.

00:04:53.110 --> 00:04:54.840 line:80%
We really came to
offer our congratulations.

00:04:54.840 --> 00:04:55.900 line:80%
Congratulations.

00:04:59.130 --> 00:05:00.260 line:80%
Please spare us.

00:05:01.550 --> 00:05:02.750 line:80%
That's all we've got.

00:05:03.430 --> 00:05:04.360 line:80%
Please spare us.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:05.630 line:80%
Get lost.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.360 line:80%
If you dare come back
and cause trouble again,

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:11.090 line:80%
you'll deserve it
even if you get beaten to death!

00:05:11.110 --> 00:05:12.670 line:80%
Let's go.

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.920 line:80%
Leave at once! Get lost!

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:18.210 line:80%
-Well done!
-Well done! Well done!

00:05:20.010 --> 00:05:21.050 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:05:23.020 --> 00:05:24.680 line:80%
So they did hurt you after all.

00:05:25.430 --> 00:05:25.990 line:80%
I'll go kill them.

00:05:25.990 --> 00:05:27.190 line:80%
They're not to blame.

00:05:28.190 --> 00:05:29.280 line:80%
Then who's to blame?

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:30.210 line:80%
Me. I'm to blame.

00:05:31.400 --> 00:05:32.430 line:80%
I sat on him.

00:05:32.750 --> 00:05:33.630 line:80%
I was part of it too.

00:05:33.630 --> 00:05:34.360 line:80%
Me too.

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:35.360 line:80%
And me.

00:05:38.990 --> 00:05:39.959 line:80%
-Alright.
-Come on.

00:05:39.959 --> 00:05:42.560 line:80%
-Here we are. Be careful.
-Excuse me. Make way.

00:05:42.750 --> 00:05:45.550 line:80%
Your uncle is to blame. He's so clumsy.

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:46.870 line:80%
I was just out buying groceries,

00:05:46.870 --> 00:05:48.720 line:80%
and he hurt him by sitting on him.

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:50.480 line:80%
Just when he was recovering.

00:05:50.630 --> 00:05:52.160 line:80%
Actually, he survived
thanks to Mr. Zhao's help.

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.560 line:80%
I should be thanking you.

00:05:54.010 --> 00:05:55.680 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, you guys go rest.

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:57.280 line:80%
I'll take care of Yan Zheng.

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:57.920 line:80%
Okay.

00:05:58.230 --> 00:06:00.400 line:80%
I'll go make some dishes
to treat everyone.

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:01.040 line:80%
Alright.

00:06:01.040 --> 00:06:01.840 line:80%
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:02.520 line:80%
Go outside.

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.160 line:80%
Yan Zheng, give me your hand.

00:06:08.610 --> 00:06:10.120 line:80%
Zhao, come out here.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:11.310 line:80%
What for?

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:13.330 line:80%
What do you think?

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.790 line:80%
But I haven't checked his pulse yet.

00:06:14.790 --> 00:06:15.720 line:80%
Forget about it.

00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:16.790 line:80%
Can't you read the room?

00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:18.110 line:80%
Read what room?

00:06:32.420 --> 00:06:34.220 line:80%
The wound on your back reopened.

00:06:34.450 --> 00:06:36.050 line:80%
There's a large bloodstain.

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:37.660 line:80%
It needs cleaning.

00:06:38.070 --> 00:06:39.550 line:80%
I-I'll do it myself.

00:06:39.570 --> 00:06:40.250 line:80%
Let me.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:54.540 line:80%
You beat those men, didn't you?

00:06:55.959 --> 00:06:57.090 line:80%
This wound of yours—

00:06:57.400 --> 00:06:58.840 line:80%
even if Mr. Zhao sat on it,

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:01.220 line:80%
it wouldn't have torn open like this.

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:03.160 line:80%
You must have fought.

00:07:04.430 --> 00:07:05.690 line:80%
With a build like that,

00:07:06.110 --> 00:07:07.190 line:80%
it's obvious that

00:07:09.070 --> 00:07:10.870 line:80%
you're trained in martial arts.

00:07:23.530 --> 00:07:25.060 line:80%
I used to be an armed escort.

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:26.890 line:80%
I traveled all over,

00:07:27.810 --> 00:07:30.200 line:80%
and just picked up some fighting skills
for self-defense.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:32.000 line:80%
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

00:07:36.430 --> 00:07:37.230 line:80%
No wonder.

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:40.550 line:80%
My father used to be an armed escort too.

00:07:40.550 --> 00:07:42.750 line:80%
He also had many old wounds like yours.

00:07:42.900 --> 00:07:43.760 line:80%
Being an escort

00:07:44.550 --> 00:07:46.750 line:80%
is truly a life-threatening business.

00:07:51.300 --> 00:07:52.150 line:80%
Bear with it.

00:07:56.070 --> 00:07:57.230 line:80%
So you were wounded

00:07:57.870 --> 00:07:59.459 line:80%
by bandits at Huchakou

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:00.430 line:80%
as well?

00:08:05.110 --> 00:08:05.840 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:09.130 --> 00:08:11.260 line:80%
There's nothing valuable in our home.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:12.780 line:80%
If they wanted to smash things, let them.

00:08:12.780 --> 00:08:13.920 line:80%
Why did you step in?

00:08:16.190 --> 00:08:17.520 line:80%
If I hadn't stepped in,

00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:20.810 line:80%
they would have taken this.

00:08:26.250 --> 00:08:29.970 line:80%
[Deed of House Sale]

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.760 line:80%
So you stepped in

00:08:47.820 --> 00:08:48.950 line:80%
for this title deed?

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:18.890 line:80%
Thanks a lot.

00:10:51.270 --> 00:10:56.170 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:10:56.250 --> 00:10:58.840 line:80%
[Episode 4]

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:02.310 line:80%
When I swung my broom today,

00:11:02.590 --> 00:11:03.800 line:80%
they all fell.

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:06.920 line:80%
Whoever I touched went down.

00:11:07.630 --> 00:11:08.690 line:80%
No wonder they say,

00:11:08.700 --> 00:11:10.620 line:80%
even a rabbit bites when cornered.

00:11:10.620 --> 00:11:11.670 line:80%
If we hadn't fought,

00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:13.120 line:80%
how would we know we were so capable?

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:14.070 line:80%
Exactly.

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:15.360 line:80%
You gentlemen

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.280 line:80%
are the Gods of War of Xigu Lane.

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:18.710 line:80%
-That's right. Come on.
-Of course.

00:11:18.710 --> 00:11:19.930 line:80%
Cheers.

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:21.000 line:80%
Drink up.

00:11:24.130 --> 00:11:27.190 line:80%
If you ask me, we're no worse than
that Marquis of Wu'an.

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:28.080 line:80%
Don't you agree?

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:29.080 line:80%
Of course.

00:11:30.630 --> 00:11:31.230 line:80%
I agree.

00:11:34.370 --> 00:11:35.060 line:80%
It's just

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:38.070 line:80%
you're a bit weak, kid.

00:11:38.090 --> 00:11:40.820 line:80%
You got injured just because
I sat on you for a bit.

00:11:41.190 --> 00:11:43.590 line:80%
Changyu, you should nourish him properly.

00:11:44.790 --> 00:11:45.670 line:80%
Uncle,

00:11:45.690 --> 00:11:47.950 line:80%
he's only like this
because his old injuries haven't healed.

00:11:47.950 --> 00:11:50.570 line:80%
Come on, let's have a drink.

00:11:51.190 --> 00:11:53.760 line:80%
Don't drink alcohol. Have tea instead.

00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:54.590 line:80%
Have some tea.

00:11:54.590 --> 00:11:56.520 line:80%
You care so much about your husband?

00:11:56.520 --> 00:11:59.980 line:80%
It's fine. A little wine won't hurt.
It improves circulation.

00:12:00.070 --> 00:12:00.800 line:80%
Zhao!

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:02.670 line:80%
Why are you making a fuss here?

00:12:02.670 --> 00:12:04.190 line:80%
He just recovered. He can't drink.

00:12:04.190 --> 00:12:05.070 line:80%
You think everyone's as reckless as you?

00:12:05.070 --> 00:12:07.000 line:80%
-Go over there.
-Zhao. Come on, come drink over here.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:07.820 line:80%
Let's drink.

00:12:07.850 --> 00:12:10.920 line:80%
Changyu, did Fan Daniu
really file a lawsuit?

00:12:11.520 --> 00:12:13.120 line:80%
Is he really that shameless?

00:12:15.830 --> 00:12:17.710 line:80%
How about we hire a lawyer?

00:12:18.590 --> 00:12:20.710 line:80%
Hiring a lawyer would be too expensive.

00:12:20.710 --> 00:12:21.970 line:80%
What should we do then?

00:12:22.760 --> 00:12:25.190 line:80%
How about talking to Song Yan?

00:12:25.940 --> 00:12:28.750 line:80%
He's the only scholar in our Xigu Lane
after all.

00:12:28.780 --> 00:12:31.760 line:80%
Even officials can't make
a provincial candidate kneel.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:34.390 line:80%
He can surely help you
with the lawsuit, Changyu.

00:12:34.390 --> 00:12:36.460 line:80%
Changyu won't ask a bad guy for help.

00:12:37.590 --> 00:12:38.670 line:80%
Changning is right.

00:12:38.670 --> 00:12:40.070 line:80%
We won't ask that ingrate for help.

00:12:40.070 --> 00:12:41.940 line:80%
Right, let's not talk about that ingrate.

00:12:41.940 --> 00:12:43.650 line:80%
Come on. Let's have a drink.

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:45.080 line:80%
Come on, buddy, drink up.

00:12:45.550 --> 00:12:46.070 line:80%
Let's drink.

00:12:46.070 --> 00:12:46.550 line:80%
Cheers.

00:12:46.590 --> 00:12:47.990 line:80%
This wine is really good.

00:12:48.040 --> 00:12:48.770 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:12:49.400 --> 00:12:50.200 line:80%
I'll help you.

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:52.550 line:80%
You?

00:13:02.310 --> 00:13:03.140 line:80%
This is everything.

00:13:03.140 --> 00:13:05.040 line:80%
These were used by my mother before.

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:06.040 line:80%
Make do with them.

00:13:07.800 --> 00:13:09.130 line:80%
I'll write down
the entire response process

00:13:09.130 --> 00:13:10.860 line:80%
and the proper legal phrasing.

00:13:11.130 --> 00:13:12.320 line:80%
Memorize it,

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:15.430 line:80%
and you'll pass the hearing
without trouble.

00:13:15.300 --> 00:13:17.480 line:80%
[Household Statutes,
Legal Code of Great Yin]

00:13:15.830 --> 00:13:17.280 line:80%
You know how to write?

00:13:17.690 --> 00:13:19.190 line:80%
And you even have knowledge of this?

00:13:19.190 --> 00:13:20.880 line:80%
I've traveled far and seen much,

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:22.410 line:80%
so I naturally picked it up.

00:13:33.940 --> 00:13:34.760 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:13:38.160 --> 00:13:39.520 line:80%
I used to think

00:13:40.230 --> 00:13:43.160 line:80%
Song Yan was the most formidable person
in the world.

00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:45.240 line:80%
I never imagined you'd be
even more impressive—

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.640 line:80%
not only skilled in martial arts,

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:48.300 line:80%
but also able to write so well.

00:13:50.850 --> 00:13:52.250 line:80%
Is he the provincial candidate

00:13:52.250 --> 00:13:54.000 line:80%
who refused to help you

00:13:54.650 --> 00:13:57.250 line:80%
even though Mrs. Zhao
shouted herself hoarse?

00:13:58.520 --> 00:14:00.720 line:80%
Why don't you go to court on behalf of me?

00:14:00.760 --> 00:14:02.520 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

00:14:02.520 --> 00:14:05.200 line:80%
only the head of the household
can appear in court.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.330 line:80%
I'm not the head of the household,

00:14:06.330 --> 00:14:07.380 line:80%
so I cannot go.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:10.800 line:80%
You're really putting me on the spot.

00:14:13.290 --> 00:14:14.420 line:80%
It's almost my turn.

00:14:14.760 --> 00:14:15.400 line:80%
Silence.

00:14:17.640 --> 00:14:20.590 line:80%
Who is the petitioner below?
And what case do you present?

00:14:20.590 --> 00:14:21.350 line:80%
State it now.

00:14:22.470 --> 00:14:23.670 line:80%
You look so imposing.

00:14:23.710 --> 00:14:25.160 line:80%
You look so imposing.

00:14:32.350 --> 00:14:33.640 line:80%
Your Honor,

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:35.950 line:80%
I am Fan Changyu,

00:14:36.640 --> 00:14:37.710 line:80%
and I'm here for...

00:14:38.060 --> 00:14:38.730 line:80%
My house.

00:14:39.660 --> 00:14:40.640 line:80%
Are your parents alive?

00:14:40.640 --> 00:14:41.550 line:80%
Both are dead.

00:14:42.060 --> 00:14:43.640 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin，

00:14:43.640 --> 00:14:44.730 line:80%
if a household has no male heir,

00:14:44.730 --> 00:14:45.950 line:80%
the house goes to the next of kin.

00:14:45.950 --> 00:14:47.160 line:80%
If the older brother dies,
the younger succeeds.

00:14:47.160 --> 00:14:48.830 line:80%
-And if the younger brother dies...
-That's nonsense!

00:14:48.830 --> 00:14:50.280 line:80%
That's nonsense.

00:14:52.710 --> 00:14:53.830 line:80%
For causing a disturbance in court,

00:14:53.830 --> 00:14:54.760 line:80%
you, Changning,

00:14:55.310 --> 00:14:56.120 line:80%
are to be flogged 10 times.

00:14:56.120 --> 00:14:57.120 line:80%
Got it.

00:14:58.630 --> 00:15:00.370 line:80%
One. Two...

00:15:00.430 --> 00:15:01.550 line:80%
You're serious?

00:15:05.160 --> 00:15:06.430 line:80%
Your Honor.

00:15:07.710 --> 00:15:09.710 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

00:15:09.710 --> 00:15:12.670 line:80%
specifically Article 17
of Extinction of a Household Circle,

00:15:12.670 --> 00:15:14.190 line:80%
when a household is extinct,
circle circle inherit,

00:15:14.190 --> 00:15:15.350 line:80%
and when there's a circle,
a circle makes the choice.

00:15:15.350 --> 00:15:15.710 line:80%
Stop.

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:16.310 line:80%
Circle...

00:15:16.590 --> 00:15:19.590 line:80%
Extinction of a Household Circle?
What's a "circle"?

00:15:20.950 --> 00:15:22.920 line:80%
I can never remember the characters.

00:15:22.920 --> 00:15:24.190 line:80%
So my mother told me

00:15:24.830 --> 00:15:25.710 line:80%
to draw a circle
for each character I don't know.

00:15:25.710 --> 00:15:26.940 line:80%
I'm used to reading like this.

00:15:26.940 --> 00:15:28.480 line:80%
[Article 17, Extinction of a Household Section,
Household Statutes, Legal Code of Great Yin]

00:15:29.800 --> 00:15:31.530 line:80%
I really can't remember these.

00:15:31.670 --> 00:15:32.530 line:80%
How about this?

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:34.710 line:80%
Let's find a sack

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:36.960 line:80%
and kidnap Fan Daniu. What do you think?

00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:38.830 line:80%
What then?

00:15:39.160 --> 00:15:40.070 line:80%
Mr. Wang said

00:15:40.430 --> 00:15:42.240 line:80%
if he's not there on the day of the trial,

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.440 line:80%
the case won't count.

00:15:50.920 --> 00:15:52.280 line:80%
Since it happened once,

00:15:52.500 --> 00:15:53.950 line:80%
it will happen again.

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:55.670 line:80%
Why not

00:15:56.300 --> 00:15:57.850 line:80%
just kill him

00:16:00.130 --> 00:16:01.600 line:80%
and be done with it?

00:16:07.030 --> 00:16:09.890 line:80%
K-Killing is against the law.

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:11.920 line:80%
L-Let's not.

00:16:16.010 --> 00:16:18.120 line:80%
Since you can't bear to be that ruthless,

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:20.190 line:80%
you'll have to suffer through it yourself.

00:16:20.190 --> 00:16:21.050 line:80%
Keep reciting.

00:16:24.090 --> 00:16:27.350 line:80%
Extinction of a Household Section,
Household Statutes, Legal Code of Great Yin.

00:16:27.350 --> 00:16:28.670 line:80%
Article 17:

00:16:28.800 --> 00:16:31.000 line:80%
"In cases of household extinctions…"

00:16:33.830 --> 00:16:35.280 line:80%
Don't be mad.

00:16:35.710 --> 00:16:37.070 line:80%
Your health comes first.

00:16:37.070 --> 00:16:38.200 line:80%
I'll keep reciting.

00:16:38.640 --> 00:16:39.300 line:80%
Never mind.

00:16:40.830 --> 00:16:42.590 line:80%
Just recite this Seven-Step Poem.

00:16:42.590 --> 00:16:44.810 line:80%
Laws are ultimately grounded in reason,

00:16:44.810 --> 00:16:46.850 line:80%
so this might be more persuasive.

00:16:47.830 --> 00:16:51.490 line:80%
Magistrate Cui is a double-ranked
scholar-official, after all.

00:16:51.950 --> 00:16:53.210 line:80%
What Seven-Step Poem?

00:16:54.710 --> 00:16:56.040 line:80%
"Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.

00:16:56.040 --> 00:16:57.470 line:80%
The beans are sobbing inside the pot.

00:16:57.470 --> 00:16:58.680 line:80%
Both of them were born from the same root.

00:16:58.680 --> 00:17:00.160 line:80%
Why rush to torment each other?"

00:17:00.160 --> 00:17:01.290 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:17:01.470 --> 00:17:04.399 line:80%
It speaks of boiling beans
with beanstalks for fuel,

00:17:04.430 --> 00:17:07.149 line:80%
a metaphor for the deadly strife
between brothers of the same father.

00:17:07.149 --> 00:17:10.240 line:80%
By extension, it condemns Fan Daniu
for abusing his brother's daughter,

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:12.040 line:80%
an act devoid of kinship and morality.

00:17:12.040 --> 00:17:13.100 line:80%
That's brilliant.

00:17:15.369 --> 00:17:18.350 line:80%
It's like this poem was originally
written for Fan Daniu.

00:17:18.350 --> 00:17:19.680 line:80%
He's not worthy of that.

00:17:24.510 --> 00:17:25.520 line:80%
What does "Fu" mean?

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:26.040 line:80%
Pot.

00:17:27.869 --> 00:17:30.400 line:80%
"Same root" must mean
having the same father.

00:17:32.230 --> 00:17:33.490 line:80%
What about "torment"?

00:17:33.830 --> 00:17:35.850 line:80%
Is it a cooking method?

00:17:35.910 --> 00:17:38.070 line:80%
It's a metaphor for killing.

00:17:42.040 --> 00:17:42.760 line:80%
Got it.

00:17:44.310 --> 00:17:45.310 line:80%
You really got it?

00:17:50.630 --> 00:17:53.110 line:80%
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

00:17:54.150 --> 00:17:55.200 line:80%
The beans

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.000 line:80%
in the pot cry out:

00:17:59.200 --> 00:18:01.520 line:80%
"we share the same father,

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:04.390 line:80%
so why kill me first?"

00:18:11.310 --> 00:18:12.310 line:80%
Is it wrong?

00:18:15.240 --> 00:18:16.700 line:80%
I wouldn't say it's wrong.

00:18:18.070 --> 00:18:19.590 line:80%
Your Honor!

00:18:19.590 --> 00:18:22.240 line:80%
Your Honor!

00:18:25.960 --> 00:18:28.870 line:80%
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

00:18:28.870 --> 00:18:31.000 line:80%
The beans in the pot cry out:

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:33.910 line:80%
"we share the same father,

00:18:33.910 --> 00:18:36.480 line:80%
so why kill me first?"

00:18:49.130 --> 00:18:53.020 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:18:49.310 --> 00:18:51.720 line:80%
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:54.310 line:80%
The beans in the pot cry out.

00:18:54.950 --> 00:18:57.200 line:80%
"we share the same father,

00:18:57.760 --> 00:19:00.800 line:80%
so why kill me first?"

00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:04.910 line:80%
Your Honor!

00:19:05.150 --> 00:19:09.680 line:80%
Your Honor!

00:19:11.150 --> 00:19:13.800 line:80%
Your Honor!

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:24.170 line:80%
Yan, where are you going?

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:29.360 line:80%
I'm just tired from studying.

00:19:29.590 --> 00:19:30.790 line:80%
I want to go for a walk.

00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:42.350 line:80%
You still have the metropolitan exam

00:19:42.380 --> 00:19:44.180 line:80%
and the palace exam ahead of you.

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:47.080 line:80%
Don't get any foolish ideas.

00:19:52.370 --> 00:19:52.890 line:80%
Okay.

00:20:02.400 --> 00:20:04.530 line:80%
Boiling beans...

00:20:55.400 --> 00:20:56.120 line:80%
Mother.

00:21:02.550 --> 00:21:03.480 line:80%
Mother.

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:06.810 line:80%
I'm so tired.

00:21:56.290 --> 00:21:57.690 line:80%
Did I wake you?

00:21:57.820 --> 00:22:00.310 line:80%
I fell asleep on your hand just now?

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:07.160 line:80%
You must be sleepy from reading too.

00:22:09.230 --> 00:22:10.660 line:80%
I totally understand.

00:22:14.580 --> 00:22:15.970 line:80%
Why did the lamp go out?

00:22:15.990 --> 00:22:17.520 line:80%
I'll go find a fire starter.

00:22:20.170 --> 00:22:22.430 line:80%
It's so late. Who's knocking at the door?

00:22:27.200 --> 00:22:28.090 line:80%
Song Yan?

00:22:28.460 --> 00:22:29.170 line:80%
Why are you here...

00:22:29.170 --> 00:22:30.030 line:80%
Let me in first.

00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:31.510 line:80%
Don't let my mother see me.

00:22:32.570 --> 00:22:33.250 line:80%
I have...

00:22:34.990 --> 00:22:35.710 line:80%
Have what?

00:22:44.650 --> 00:22:45.280 line:80%
Changyu.

00:22:46.150 --> 00:22:47.280 line:80%
I'm risking the crime of
disobeying my elders

00:22:47.280 --> 00:22:48.650 line:80%
and committing a great offense
to come here

00:22:48.650 --> 00:22:50.180 line:80%
and help you keep this home.

00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:51.760 line:80%
What?

00:22:52.630 --> 00:22:53.630 line:80%
A few days ago,

00:22:53.830 --> 00:22:55.040 line:80%
I thought for a long time

00:22:55.040 --> 00:22:57.040 line:80%
and finally came up with a solution.

00:22:58.390 --> 00:22:59.480 line:80%
I came to tell you

00:23:00.260 --> 00:23:02.720 line:80%
that I'm willing to take you
as my concubine.

00:23:07.430 --> 00:23:09.300 line:80%
Are you out of your mind?

00:23:09.330 --> 00:23:10.860 line:80%
Don't celebrate too early.

00:23:10.970 --> 00:23:12.730 line:80%
I can only try to beg the Magistrate

00:23:12.730 --> 00:23:14.220 line:80%
to grant me a special dispensation.

00:23:14.220 --> 00:23:15.960 line:80%
Hopefully, with my status
as a provincial candidate,

00:23:15.960 --> 00:23:17.960 line:80%
the Magistrate will do me this favor.

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:20.360 line:80%
This way, you can keep your house

00:23:20.380 --> 00:23:22.380 line:80%
and get the title you've wished for.

00:23:24.530 --> 00:23:25.330 line:80%
Song Yan.

00:23:26.480 --> 00:23:28.480 line:80%
You think just because I'm a butcher girl,

00:23:28.480 --> 00:23:31.050 line:80%
and you're lowering yourself
to take me as a concubine,

00:23:31.050 --> 00:23:32.920 line:80%
I should be thanking you, right?

00:23:33.350 --> 00:23:34.680 line:80%
That's not what I meant.

00:23:35.170 --> 00:23:36.410 line:80%
I just never expected

00:23:36.990 --> 00:23:38.220 line:80%
that for this house,

00:23:38.630 --> 00:23:40.040 line:80%
you would act so rashly

00:23:40.370 --> 00:23:42.530 line:80%
and give yourself to
a crippled refugee from Chongzhou.

00:23:42.530 --> 00:23:43.660 line:80%
A crippled refugee?

00:23:43.960 --> 00:23:44.520 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:46.950 --> 00:23:48.610 line:80%
Song Yan, I'm really curious.

00:23:50.010 --> 00:23:52.310 line:80%
What gives you the right
to look down on him like that?

00:23:52.310 --> 00:23:53.910 line:80%
Even setting aside the fact that he's both
learned and skilled in martial arts,

00:23:53.910 --> 00:23:54.660 line:80%
educated and reasonable,

00:23:54.660 --> 00:23:55.480 line:80%
just in terms of looks alone,

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:57.140 line:80%
Yan Zheng's 10 times better than you.

00:23:57.140 --> 00:23:58.210 line:80%
Most importantly,

00:23:59.050 --> 00:24:00.940 line:80%
he knows how to appreciate
what others do for him.

00:24:00.940 --> 00:24:02.610 line:80%
He understands my difficulties

00:24:02.610 --> 00:24:04.740 line:80%
and is willing to marry into my family.

00:24:05.070 --> 00:24:06.440 line:80%
Even when he was hurt,

00:24:06.470 --> 00:24:08.030 line:80%
he still stood up for me

00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:10.210 line:80%
and helped me seek justice.

00:24:10.540 --> 00:24:11.540 line:80%
Such devotion—

00:24:12.760 --> 00:24:14.960 line:80%
isn't it 1,000 times better than yours?

00:24:15.440 --> 00:24:18.380 line:80%
You're just unwilling to let go now

00:24:18.970 --> 00:24:21.920 line:80%
and want to earn a good reputation
in the neighborhood,

00:24:21.920 --> 00:24:23.530 line:80%
so you had no choice but to come here.

00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:24.220 line:80%
Song Yan.

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:26.360 line:80%
You just can't miss out on

00:24:26.920 --> 00:24:28.630 line:80%
any good thing in this world, can you?

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:29.720 line:80%
It's not like that.

00:24:29.850 --> 00:24:31.550 line:80%
My feelings for you are sincere.

00:24:31.550 --> 00:24:33.100 line:80%
I, Song Yan, hold your hand now,

00:24:33.100 --> 00:24:34.360 line:80%
and swear to Heaven...

00:24:36.980 --> 00:24:37.420 line:80%
I...

00:24:42.530 --> 00:24:43.460 line:80%
Who are you?

00:24:44.280 --> 00:24:45.210 line:80%
Who am I, you ask?

00:24:51.130 --> 00:24:52.400 line:80%
The crippled refugee.

00:24:57.400 --> 00:24:58.890 line:80%
I think of you every night,

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:01.570 line:80%
and this is how little womanly virtue
you have?

00:25:01.570 --> 00:25:02.860 line:80%
Who are you to me?

00:25:03.040 --> 00:25:04.950 line:80%
Why should I observe any womanly virtue?

00:25:04.950 --> 00:25:06.910 line:80%
You've disregarded all sense of
decorum and morality!

00:25:06.910 --> 00:25:08.350 line:80%
It's simply scandalous!

00:25:08.540 --> 00:25:09.610 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

00:25:09.610 --> 00:25:10.610 line:80%
those who commit adultery are guilty of
fornication and shall receive 80 lashes!

00:25:10.610 --> 00:25:12.760 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

00:25:12.760 --> 00:25:15.200 line:80%
your breaking into a private residence
at night counts as burglary,

00:25:15.200 --> 00:25:16.800 line:80%
and death would be deserved.

00:25:16.920 --> 00:25:18.140 line:80%
See for yourself.

00:25:21.190 --> 00:25:22.640 line:80%
This is my husband,

00:25:23.490 --> 00:25:25.960 line:80%
the man lawfully married to
me, Fan Changyu.

00:25:31.550 --> 00:25:32.480 line:80%
You two...

00:25:32.730 --> 00:25:34.330 line:80%
You two are just shameless!

00:25:34.520 --> 00:25:35.830 line:80%
Shameless!

00:25:36.890 --> 00:25:39.500 line:80%
To commit such acts against public morals—

00:25:39.980 --> 00:25:41.630 line:80%
this is simply scandalous!

00:25:59.630 --> 00:26:01.630 line:80%
Why did I kiss him?

00:26:02.870 --> 00:26:06.000 line:80%
If I scared him so much that
he won't marry into my family,

00:26:06.430 --> 00:26:09.240 line:80%
wouldn't I be losing a great deal
for a small gain?

00:26:34.710 --> 00:26:36.910 line:80%
It's all that bastard Song Yan's fault.

00:26:37.970 --> 00:26:39.150 line:80%
Bastard.

00:26:39.980 --> 00:26:41.980 line:80%
Bastard. Bastard. Bastard.

00:26:53.130 --> 00:26:55.260 line:80%
What on earth was that woman thinking?

00:26:55.760 --> 00:27:00.100 line:80%
[Only My Virtue is Fragrant]

00:26:56.360 --> 00:26:58.760 line:80%
All for that pathetic
matrilocal husband?

00:27:14.580 --> 00:27:16.650 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, where's Mr. Zhao?

00:27:16.680 --> 00:27:17.680 line:80%
He went to town.

00:27:27.790 --> 00:27:29.050 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, you're back.

00:27:29.510 --> 00:27:31.570 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, I need to go out for a bit.

00:27:32.690 --> 00:27:33.220 line:80%
Changyu.

00:27:33.230 --> 00:27:33.880 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:39.350 line:80%
This young couple...

00:27:39.350 --> 00:27:42.160 line:80%
Why are they acting like
they're avoiding each other?

00:27:42.160 --> 00:27:44.910 line:80%
Brides get nervous before the wedding.

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:47.140 line:80%
Even though Changyu has a boyish nature,

00:27:47.140 --> 00:27:48.490 line:80%
she gets shy too.

00:27:49.090 --> 00:27:51.240 line:80%
So you were also shy before marrying me?

00:27:51.240 --> 00:27:52.040 line:80%
Shy?

00:27:52.220 --> 00:27:54.750 line:80%
-I didn't even know who to cry to!
-Look at you.

00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:56.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:27:56.110 --> 00:27:58.150 line:80%
Yan Zheng, you're awake.

00:27:58.870 --> 00:28:00.150 line:80%
Changyu just went out.

00:28:00.170 --> 00:28:01.000 line:80%
I know.

00:28:02.010 --> 00:28:03.280 line:80%
I need to talk to you about something,
Mr. Zhao.

00:28:03.280 --> 00:28:04.430 line:80%
I want to talk to you too.

00:28:04.430 --> 00:28:05.190 line:80%
Come on.

00:28:05.480 --> 00:28:06.010 line:80%
This way.

00:28:07.200 --> 00:28:08.000 line:80%
Be careful.

00:28:10.270 --> 00:28:12.310 line:80%
Those essays you wrote

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:14.760 line:80%
can sell for so much money?

00:28:16.160 --> 00:28:17.340 line:80%
Is this a lot?

00:28:17.700 --> 00:28:19.290 line:80%
Twenty taels isn't a lot?

00:28:19.690 --> 00:28:22.690 line:80%
I almost thought the bookshop owner
had lost his mind.

00:28:24.840 --> 00:28:27.560 line:80%
[Wuqi has arrived at
Lin'an Four Seasons Bookshop]

00:28:27.650 --> 00:28:30.250 line:80%
What kind of divine calligraphy
did you write?

00:28:32.790 --> 00:28:34.960 line:80%
I've traveled a lot and seen much.

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:37.600 line:80%
I just casually wrote some nonsense
to bluff people.

00:28:37.600 --> 00:28:38.550 line:80%
I didn't expect

00:28:38.570 --> 00:28:40.700 line:80%
the bookshop owner to actually buy it.

00:28:41.340 --> 00:28:43.540 line:80%
That's pure profit.

00:28:43.940 --> 00:28:46.140 line:80%
Write a few more. I'll sell them for you.

00:28:47.690 --> 00:28:49.560 line:80%
I was only imitating the masters.

00:28:49.830 --> 00:28:52.240 line:80%
If I write more, I might be exposed.

00:28:52.270 --> 00:28:53.530 line:80%
It's not appropriate.

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:56.700 line:80%
Right, right. Can't be showy.

00:28:57.500 --> 00:28:59.170 line:80%
But writing once in a while

00:28:59.360 --> 00:29:01.620 line:80%
would make enough for a year's expenses.

00:29:02.890 --> 00:29:05.750 line:80%
This little bit of silver
is enough for a whole year?

00:29:06.130 --> 00:29:07.680 line:80%
For a humble household,

00:29:07.710 --> 00:29:09.630 line:80%
if you budget carefully,

00:29:09.660 --> 00:29:11.200 line:80%
it's even enough for 2 or 3 years.

00:29:11.200 --> 00:29:13.270 line:80%
It seems I miscalculated after all.

00:29:15.310 --> 00:29:16.960 line:80%
About me selling essays,

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:19.020 line:80%
please help me keep it a secret, Mr. Zhao.

00:29:19.020 --> 00:29:19.930 line:80%
Don't tell anyone.

00:29:19.930 --> 00:29:20.730 line:80%
I understand.

00:29:21.150 --> 00:29:22.560 line:80%
I'm discreet.

00:29:22.590 --> 00:29:24.320 line:80%
I know how to keep my mouth shut.

00:29:25.940 --> 00:29:27.110 line:80%
That little fool

00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:30.500 line:80%
actually got herself a husband
who knows how to make money.

00:29:30.500 --> 00:29:34.350 line:80%
Her hard times are over now.
Truly blessed.

00:29:53.430 --> 00:29:54.260 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:54.470 --> 00:29:55.480 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:29:55.500 --> 00:29:57.300 line:80%
What took you so long?

00:29:57.830 --> 00:29:59.760 line:80%
Come and see who's waiting for you.

00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:01.360 line:80%
Mrs. Chen, you're here.

00:30:01.680 --> 00:30:02.950 line:80%
Changyu.

00:30:04.860 --> 00:30:06.120 line:80%
Open it and take a look.

00:30:09.120 --> 00:30:10.310 line:80%
Come on, open it.

00:30:28.830 --> 00:30:29.390 line:80%
This...

00:30:31.160 --> 00:30:31.960 line:80%
For me?

00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:36.930 line:80%
Didn't you say you were only making one
for the groom?

00:30:37.090 --> 00:30:39.290 line:80%
Girls always side with their husbands.

00:30:39.650 --> 00:30:41.430 line:80%
I deliberately saved some fabric

00:30:41.430 --> 00:30:43.190 line:80%
and borrowed some scraps

00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:43.790 line:80%
to make

00:30:44.030 --> 00:30:45.370 line:80%
a set for you too.

00:30:46.120 --> 00:30:46.950 line:80%
Thank you so much.

00:30:46.950 --> 00:30:48.020 line:80%
