00:33:08.560 --> 00:33:10.160 line:80%
Why is she sitting on the bed?

00:33:22.580 --> 00:33:24.290 line:80%
Why is he sitting next to me?

00:33:31.720 --> 00:33:33.200 line:80%
Let's go try them on together then.

00:33:33.200 --> 00:33:34.080 line:80%
Sure.

00:33:37.530 --> 00:33:38.590 line:80%
Let's go together.

00:33:38.850 --> 00:33:39.440 line:80%
Let's go.

00:33:45.620 --> 00:33:46.430 line:80%
Let's go.

00:33:46.830 --> 00:33:47.590 line:80%
Let's go.

00:33:48.240 --> 00:33:49.830 line:80%
Why isn't he moving?

