00:34:48.610 --> 00:34:49.760 line:80%
He probably didn't see it.

00:34:49.760 --> 00:34:52.959 line:80%
He definitely didn't see it.
Didn't see it, didn't see it.

00:34:53.900 --> 00:34:55.920 line:80%
So embarrassing.

