00:41:15.630 --> 00:41:17.500 line:80%
-Wonderful!
-Excellent!

00:41:17.520 --> 00:41:20.210 line:80%
-Wonderful!
-Excellent!

00:41:20.890 --> 00:41:22.120 line:80%
Wonderful!

