00:45:09.640 --> 00:45:10.680 line:80%
Changyu, you've had a long day.

00:45:10.680 --> 00:45:11.820 line:80%
Go back and rest early.

00:45:11.820 --> 00:45:12.300 line:80%
Okay.

00:45:12.330 --> 00:45:12.990 line:80%
